5.0.1
---------
* use layer3domain from .ndcli for more commands (#236)

5.0.0-rc1
---------
* fix missing dry-run options for modifying commands (#87)

* add environment variables NDCLI_USERNAME and NDCLI_SERVER
* add environment variable NDCLI_CONFIG and NDCLI_COOKIEPATH
* add environment variable NDCLI_LAYER3DOMAIN
* add option layer3domain to config
* create a cookie file for each user
* add command `modify container set layer3domain` (#124)
* add command `modify pool set owning-user-group`
* add command `modify pool remove owning-user-group`
* add command `modify pool set layer3domain` (#123)
* add command `modify layer3domain set type`
* add option layer3domain to `history ipblock` (#183)
